Class CustomGetOperationCompletedListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.etouch.taf.tools.tfsclient.event.CustomGetOperationCompletedListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class CustomGetOperationCompletedListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.microsoft.tfs.core.clients.versioncontrol.events.OperationCompletedListener
    The listener interface for receiving customGetOperationCompleted events. The class that is interested in processing a customGetOperationCompleted event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addCustomGetOperationCompletedListener method. When the customGetOperationCompleted event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
